Various "to a diamond" modifiers.

sdr> /program = C4
C4
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.PARALLEL_RH_WAVES)
| 1B^  1Gv  2B^  2Gv
| 
| 4G^  4Bv  3G^  3Bv
sdr> cross to a diamond
|      1B>
| 
| 2Bv  2G<  3G^
| 
| 1Gv  4G>  4B^
| 
|      3B<
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.PARALLEL_RH_WAVES)
| 1B^  1Gv  2B^  2Gv
| 
| 4G^  4Bv  3G^  3Bv
sdr> cross to an hourglass
|        1B>
| 
| 2Bv            3G^
|      4G^  2Gv
| 1Gv            4B^
| 
|        3B<
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.PARALLEL_RH_WAVES)
| 1B^  1Gv  2B^  2Gv
| 
| 4G^  4Bv  3G^  3Bv
sdr> cross to a z
|      1B>  3G<
| 
| 2B>  2G<
| 
|      4G>  4B<
| 
| 1G>  3B<
sdr> /setFormation(FormationList.PARALLEL_RH_WAVES)
| 1B^  1Gv  2B^  2Gv
| 
| 4G^  4Bv  3G^  3Bv
sdr> cross to an interlocked diamond
|      1B>
| 
| 2Bv  4G>  3G^
| 
| 1Gv  2G<  4B^
| 
|      3B<
sdr> /exit
